ed="T" n="0891a07"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0891a07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>天台山國清寺<persName key="A001563">道邃</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0891a08"/><persName key="A001563">釋道邃</persName>，不知何許人也。幽識遠晤，執志有<lb
ed="T" n="0891a09"/>恒，懸解<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1343"/>真宗，不由邪術。末傳隋<persName key="A001301">智者</persName>教<lb
ed="T" n="0891a10"/>道，素得玄微<ptr type="glossary" target="#g773"/>，<persName key="A001307">荊溪</persName>之門，<anchor xml:id="beg0891sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>沓</sic><corr>杳</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0891sgsz2"/>難窺望。<date key="j20011912005747" notAfter-iso="+0779-06-13" notBefore-iso="+0766-12-22"><name>大曆</name>中</date><lb
ed="T" n="0891a11"/><persName key="A001307">湛然師</persName>委付《止觀輔行記》，得以敷揚，若神<lb
ed="T" n="0891a12"/>驥之可以致遠也。于時同門<persName key="A009613">元浩</persName>逈知畏服，<lb
ed="T" n="0891a13"/>不能爭長矣。<date key="j20151182015139" notAfter-iso="+0805-02-28" notBefore-iso="+0805-02-07"><name>貞元</name>二十一年</date>，<placeName key="PL000000048414">日本國</placeName>沙門<lb
ed="T" n="0891a14"/><persName key="A001177">最澄</persName>者，亦<placeName key="PL000000055413">東夷</placeName>卉服中，剛決明敏僧也。泛溟<lb
ed="T" n="0891a15"/>涬，達<placeName key="PL000000000197">江東</placeName>，慕<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>之法門，求<persName key="A001301">顗師</persName>之禪決。<lb
ed="T" n="0891a16"/>屬<persName key="A001563">邃</persName>講訓，委曲指教，<persName key="A001177">澄</persName>得旨矣。乃盡繕寫<lb
ed="T" n="0891a17"/>一行教法東歸。慮其或問從何而聞，得誰<lb
ed="T" n="0891a18"/>所印？俾防疑誤，乃造邦伯作援證焉。時<lb
ed="T" n="0891a19"/><placeName key="PL000000014901">台州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A013862">陸淳</persName>判云：「<persName key="A001177">最澄</persName>闍梨，形雖異域，性<lb
ed="T" n="0891a20"/>實同源，特稟生知，觸類玄解。遠傳<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>教<lb
ed="T" n="0891a21"/>旨，又遇龍象<persName key="A001563">邃公</persName>，總萬行於一心，了殊塗<lb
ed="T" n="0891a22"/>於三觀，親承祕密，理絕名言。猶慮他方學<lb
ed="T" n="0891a23"/>徒未能信受，所請印記，安可不任為憑<lb
ed="T" n="0891a24"/>云。」<persName key="A001177">澄</persName>泛海到國，齎教法指一山為<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0891a25"/>號一寺為<placeName key="PL000000014664">國清</placeName>，風行電照，斯教大行。倭僧<lb
ed="T" n="0891a26"/>遙尊<persName key="A001563">邃</persName>為祖師。後終于<placeName key="PL000000014664">住寺</placeName>焉。</p>
